main event: On 25 Oct 61, a witness observed a circular object with a blinking, pulsating light at Patrick AFB, Florida.
interesting points: The object was seen intermittently over a few minutes., The sighting lasted approximately 10 seconds., The object was described as white and circular., No sound was heard during the observation., The flight path of the object was straight and level from east to west.
sighted object: circular object with blinking, pulsating light
witness description: A pilot with 3502 hours flying time, reliability considered to be excellent.
